{"version":"NotebookV1","origId":1083584440950763,"name":"10-1 Data Cleansing","language":"python","commands":[{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950764,"guid":"d5ec1f8b-d5fe-4a2e-9a41-416278057827","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":1.0,"command":"\n%md-sandbox\n# Data Cleansing with Airbnb\n\nWe're going to start by doing some exploratory data analysis & cleansing. We will be using the SF Airbnb rental dataset from [Inside Airbnb](http://insideairbnb.com/get-the-data.html).\n\n<img src=\"http://insideairbnb.com/images/insideairbnb_graphic_site_1200px.png\" style=\"width:800px\"/>","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"fc7ce6ab-a443-4e5c-bde7-9edc3c419963"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950765,"guid":"56101891-29c6-4e7d-a334-fe4cbd8a4d41","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":2.0,"command":"%md\nLet's load the SF Airbnb dataset (comment out each of the options if you want to see what they do).","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"f9035760-77ad-4db7-b7c6-2484493290fa"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950766,"guid":"ab4949d2-0d68-4bd8-94b4-b3410d089c47","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":3.0,"command":"filePath = \"/databricks-datasets/learning-spark-v2/sf-airbnb/sf-airbnb.csv\"\n\nrawDF = spark.read.csv(filePath, header=\"true\", inferSchema=\"true\", multiLine=\"true\", escape='\"')\n\ndisplay(rawDF)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"26750","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"cf087513-99f0-41df-ae0d-ba0358bd7704"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950767,"guid":"bb1e9890-be5b-4b7f-b8f7-d71922b86282","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":4.0,"command":"rawDF.columns","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"c50b3295-1f49-436a-a85f-4175b9bdbdda"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950768,"guid":"efdaaf2d-361e-49e1-a573-1f487abff170","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":5.0,"command":"%md\nFor the sake of simplicity, only keep certain columns from this dataset. We will talk about feature selection later.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"ec41d90e-d891-46f2-a67d-d4a4fd4bc84c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950769,"guid":"96d31f88-4a7e-4a5e-9367-c937a1c84643","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":6.0,"command":"columnsToKeep = [\n  \"host_is_superhost\",\n  \"cancellation_policy\",\n  \"instant_bookable\",\n  \"host_total_listings_count\",\n  \"neighbourhood_cleansed\",\n  \"latitude\",\n  \"longitude\",\n  \"property_type\",\n  \"room_type\",\n  \"accommodates\",\n  \"bathrooms\",\n  \"bedrooms\",\n  \"beds\",\n  \"bed_type\",\n  \"minimum_nights\",\n  \"number_of_reviews\",\n  \"review_scores_rating\",\n  \"review_scores_accuracy\",\n  \"review_scores_cleanliness\",\n  \"review_scores_checkin\",\n  \"review_scores_communication\",\n  \"review_scores_location\",\n  \"review_scores_value\",\n  \"price\"]\n\nbaseDF = rawDF.select(columnsToKeep)\nbaseDF.cache().count()\ndisplay(baseDF)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"3656","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"901f2107-72f9-4aad-95f8-e6b17a85c30c"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950770,"guid":"e407f650-1a2a-4e6f-a545-18071ec0b33e","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":7.0,"command":"%md\n## Fixing Data Types\n\nTake a look at the schema above. You'll notice that the `price` field got picked up as string. For our task, we need it to be a numeric (double type) field. \n\nLet's fix that.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"786d54a6-085c-49fc-8754-18fe7c76d192"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950771,"guid":"0ef142b3-cd0f-499b-a3f2-f8d946203169","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":8.0,"command":"from pyspark.sql.functions import col, translate\n\nfixedPriceDF = baseDF.withColumn(\"price\", translate(col(\"price\"), \"$,\", \"\").cast(\"double\"))\n\ndisplay(fixedPriceDF)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"3656","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"3a86ec78-f534-4342-b6aa-e9d9e7498917"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950772,"guid":"2b56d797-2225-4808-ab38-c805bddf8107","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":9.0,"command":"%md\n## Summary statistics\n\nTwo options:\n* describe\n* summary (describe + IQR)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"e2e1abe3-0f98-41f0-9388-9651e02c16c5"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950773,"guid":"a8773fe4-663f-4b59-8259-219a86ad2299","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":10.0,"command":"display(fixedPriceDF.describe())","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"4142","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"51ab62e0-c88a-43d2-8dc3-1ced5ea513eb"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950774,"guid":"eee68f58-f1de-471b-937f-2b0f732ed7be","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":11.0,"command":"display(fixedPriceDF.summary())","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"4142","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"e79ab6cf-d5f3-4832-a933-40778191039e"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950775,"guid":"4d023f52-5709-4f9d-b616-ebc3e9577727","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":12.0,"command":"%md\n## Nulls\n\nThere are a lot of different ways to handle null values. Sometimes, null can actually be a key indicator of the thing you are trying to predict (e.g. if you don't fill in certain portions of a form, probability of it getting approved decreases).\n\nSome ways to handle nulls:\n* Drop any records that contain nulls\n* Numeric:\n  * Replace them with mean/median/zero/etc.\n* Categorical:\n  * Replace them with the mode\n  * Create a special category for null\n* Use techniques like ALS which are designed to impute missing values\n  \n**If you do ANY imputation techniques for categorical/numerical features, you MUST include an additional field specifying that field was imputed (think about why this is necessary)**","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"c4664895-46b7-4a4e-856f-b62e6664285e"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950776,"guid":"20050129-fb6f-4c9d-8f51-21c9e9259672","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":13.0,"command":"%md\nThere are a few nulls in the categorical feature `host_is_superhost`. Let's get rid of those rows where any of these columns is null.\n\nSparkML's Imputer (will cover below) does not support imputation for categorical features, so this is the simplest approach for the time being.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"42f8e624-0b11-4fca-8aad-0aad073be407"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950777,"guid":"9f47c0c4-28e0-433e-bee2-87c14e2e84be","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":14.0,"command":"noNullsDF = fixedPriceDF.na.drop(subset=[\"host_is_superhost\"])","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"557f5149-9db4-4012-a960-a4e819c5761d"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950778,"guid":"a40fabc9-b03b-459f-804d-f3a27c36d58d","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":15.0,"command":"%md\n## Impute: Cast to Double\n\nSparkML's `Imputer` requires all fields be of type double [Python](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/python/pyspark.ml.html#pyspark.ml.feature.Imputer)/[Scala](https://spark.apache.org/docs/latest/api/scala/#org.apache.spark.ml.feature.Imputer). Let's cast all integer fields to double.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"f2ccaa62-a19e-4ee0-9b13-d33cd9b53edf"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950779,"guid":"0e8f7a2a-abb2-40fd-aeea-00cbde460335","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":16.0,"command":"from pyspark.sql.functions import col\nfrom pyspark.sql.types import IntegerType\n\nintegerColumns = [x.name for x in baseDF.schema.fields if x.dataType == IntegerType()]\ndoublesDF = noNullsDF\n\nfor c in integerColumns:\n  doublesDF = doublesDF.withColumn(c, col(c).cast(\"double\"))\n\ncolumns = \"\\n - \".join(integerColumns)\nprint(f\"Columns converted from Integer to Double:\\n - {columns}\")","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"08fc6cdb-4322-4a6c-b11f-e6316068332f"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950780,"guid":"6233b300-ad16-4834-a7cf-15f9475c0e1c","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":17.0,"command":"%md\nAdd in dummy variable if we will impute any value.","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"57e8e147-85fd-4351-874f-f696d873d48f"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950781,"guid":"6b4caeaa-3eda-4469-b667-78b8a88099ce","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":18.0,"command":"from pyspark.sql.functions import when\n\nimputeCols = [\n  \"bedrooms\",\n  \"bathrooms\",\n  \"beds\", \n  \"review_scores_rating\",\n  \"review_scores_accuracy\",\n  \"review_scores_cleanliness\",\n  \"review_scores_checkin\",\n  \"review_scores_communication\",\n  \"review_scores_location\",\n  \"review_scores_value\"\n]\n\nfor c in imputeCols:\n  doublesDF = doublesDF.withColumn(c + \"_na\", when(col(c).isNull(), 1.0).otherwise(0.0))","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"auto","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"02f5317f-6ab1-4ad5-ac55-2d107fbf6077"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950782,"guid":"393c9883-c143-4f15-9380-a6de1bfd2cc8","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":19.0,"command":"display(doublesDF.describe())","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType":null,"error":null,"workflows":[],"startTime":0,"submitTime":0,"finishTime":0,"collapsed":false,"bindings":{},"inputWidgets":{},"displayType":"table","width":"6151","height":"auto","xColumns":null,"yColumns":null,"pivotColumns":null,"pivotAggregation":null,"useConsistentColors":false,"customPlotOptions":{},"commentThread":[],"commentsVisible":false,"parentHierarchy":[],"diffInserts":[],"diffDeletes":[],"globalVars":{},"latestUser":"a user","latestUserId":null,"commandTitle":"","showCommandTitle":false,"hideCommandCode":false,"hideCommandResult":false,"isLockedInExamMode":false,"iPythonMetadata":null,"streamStates":{},"datasetPreviewNameToCmdIdMap":{},"tableResultSubCmdIds":[],"tableResultIndex":null,"nuid":"b3114d1b-3b6a-4010-8f9e-4dcf2686e100"},{"version":"CommandV1","origId":1083584440950783,"guid":"3461aa38-063e-41d4-b152-5bb93bfbe7b5","subtype":"command","commandType":"auto","position":20.0,"command":"from pyspark.ml.feature import Imputer\n\nimputer = Imputer(strategy=\"median\", inputCols=imputeCols, outputCols=imputeCols)\n\nimputedDF = imputer.fit(doublesDF).transform(doublesDF)","commandVersion":0,"state":"error","results":null,"errorSummary":null,"errorTraceType